  schema:name "Fediverse" ;
  schema:description "The **fediverse** (a portmanteau of *federated* and *universe*) is the network of interconnected servers that communicate through open protocols — principally [ActivityPub](../../topics/activitypub/index.md) — to provide social networking, blogging, media hosting, and other services without centralized ownership." ;
